{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Solve Puzzles</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1110620/extras/puzzles.gif?t=1734611282\" />Solve challenging color based puzzles. Carry the lessons you learn from each puzzle with you for the rest of the game.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Explore The World</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1110620/extras/unlock-fast.gif?t=1734611282\" />Unlock new areas of the hub world and  gain access to new puzzle mechanics! You'll learn to use the color changers, teleporters, circuits and more. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Chat With Locals</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1110620/extras/dialogue.gif?t=1734611282\" />Some folks want to help you solve the puzzles! Some would rather you left the puzzles alone. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Undo Your Mistakes, Control Time</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1110620/extras/undo-redo.gif?t=1734611282\" /> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You can undo any mistake with the press of a button, and you can rewind, pause, or fast-forward time to suit your needs. Way of Rhea has hard puzzles, but forgiving mechanics--no combat or platforming challenges here.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">End Game</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1110620/extras/difficult.gif?t=1734611282\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Way of Rhea starts out fairly easy, but the difficulty builds over  time--use everything you've learned to beat the challenging end game!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Play On Steam Deck!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1110620/extras/steamdeck-rendering.jpg?t=1734611282\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">I test every build on Steam Deck!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Aspect Ratios</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The game is currently letter-boxed on non 16:9 aspect ratio monitors. It's tricky to get this right for a 2D game--if we just allow arbitrary aspect ratios, then the camera will point outside the level bounds, or reveal secrets or puzzle elements you're not supposed to see yet. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">I'm not super happy about that. If the game does well enough I may be able to create a patch down the line where I do a pass over each puzzle and make custom camera frames for a few more common aspect ratios, but I can't make any promises right now! </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Join My Discord</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">If you have feedback or just need a hint, the quickest way to reach me is our Discord, linked in the post on the forums.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Future games and beta testing opportunities are announced there, and it's a great place to chat with other players. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- Mason</p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Beginner's Luck","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1110620/5f079a38ce3d3a072e1182cf93323617e96098bd.jpg"},{"name":"Out of the Woods","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1110620/a7089f60a80c073b9fd02cd816e1e1de0d6c1d3a.jpg"},{"name":"Ice Puzzles Go Brrrrrrrrrr","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1110620/8ce83a16e1f283c9299902d771b6adfb9c98f3eb.jpg"},{"name":"You may pass.","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1110620/1313e4d2bcf0f31cfc75bc7c587b91efe048d4b3.jpg"},{"name":"PhD in Puzzles","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1110620/2