bitrary aspect ratios, then the camera will point outside the level bounds, or reveal secrets or puzzle elements you're not supposed to see yet. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">I'm not super happy about that. If the game does well enough I may be able to create a patch down the line where I do a pass over each puzzle and make custom camera frames for a few more common aspect ratios, but I can't make any promises right now! </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Join My Discord</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">If you have feedback or just need a hint, the quickest way to reach me is our Discord, linked in the post on the forums.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Future games and beta testing opportunities are announced there, and it's a great place to chat with other players. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- Mason</p>","developers":["Games by Mason LLC"],"genres":[{"description":"Adventure","id":"25"},{"description":"Indie","id":"23"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1110620/header.jpg?t=1734611282","is_free":false,"linux_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>OS:</strong> Ubuntu 22.04.3 LTS<br></li><li><strong>Processor:</strong> 1.4 GHz<br></li><li><strong>Memory:</strong> 2 GB RAM<br></li><li><strong>Graphics:</strong> 1024 MB VRAM<br></li><li><strong>Storage:</strong> 1 GB available space</li></ul>","recommended":"<strong>Recommended:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>OS:</strong> Ubuntu 22.04.3 LTS<br></li><li><strong>Processor:</strong> 2.0 GHz<br></li><li><strong>Memory:</strong> 4 GB RAM<br></li><li><strong>Graphics:</strong> 1024 MB VRAM<br></li><li><strong>Storage:</strong> 1 GB available space</li></ul>"},"mac_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>","recommended":"<strong>Recommended:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Memory:</strong> 2 GB RAM</li></ul>"},"movies"